# Keep the ~6GB monorepo working tree out of the Docker build context. The
# gateway build installs deps and builds inside the image, so none of this is
# needed — excluding it slashes context transfer and prevents stale artifacts
# from leaking into layers.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/build
.git
.github

# Local data / secrets — never ship into the build context or image layers.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/data
**/*.db
**/*.db-*
**/SEED-BACKUP.txt

# Noise
**/*.log
**/coverage
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
